node.text:
How are we sleeping during COVID-19? 
I attended the "sleeping through an emerging pandemic" symposium at virtual #SLEEP2020.

In adults
üîéDr. Robillard found:
‚òëÔ∏è Serious sleep difficulties in adults increased from 36% pre covid-19 to 51% during the pandemic
‚òëÔ∏èWake time was 30min later ü•≥
‚òëÔ∏è Factors making you at-risk for poor sleep during the pandemic included: being female, employed, having family responsibilities, waking up earlier, chronic illnesses, higher stress levels, chronic drinking, and lots of TV use
üîéDr. Morin found:
‚òëÔ∏èSome are sleeping better (24%) ü•≥
‚òëÔ∏èSome are sleeping worse related to insomnia (32%)
‚òëÔ∏è Adults are napping twice as much ü•≥

In Youth
üîéDr. Forest found
‚òëÔ∏èYouth (ages 12-25) are sleeping better especially on weekdays by going to bed 1 hour later but sleeping in 2 hours. This is likely more in line with their circadian rhythms and more evidence to #startschoollater. ü•≥
‚òëÔ∏è Those who were 12-17 especially did well by improving their sleep quality and reducing daytime sleepiness. ü•≥
‚òëÔ∏èThose who were older (18-25) didn't sleep quite as well. They had more difficulty falling asleep, increased awakenings, and more nightmares. This could be potentially related to more responsibilities and stressors.

Bottom line: there are many individual factors that influence how we sleep  during a pandemic. Finding ways that help YOU üí§ BETTER are important. 

Here is what I found to help me manage stress and sleep better:
‚òëÔ∏è Moderate/vigorous exercise outside in am for 45min every other day. With walking or yoga in between days
‚òëÔ∏è Nature
‚òëÔ∏èNon-alcoholic beer. I found üç∫ that tastes good without the detrimental impact on üí§. I feel like the ritual of having a beer (frosty mug required) helps me after a stressful day and I don't really miss the alcohol.
‚òëÔ∏èI try to go for green tea üçµ after a poor night's sleep. Reason being, I want to be able to take a nap or fall asleep earlier that night. Even if I just drink a half caffeinated coffee, I find that I'm wired and makes it more difficult to stay focused and fall asleep easily.

How did you sleep during lock down?

node.text:
What will you remember most about life in the time of COVID-19? Whether it’s suffering from or losing someone to the disease itself or the heartbreak of distancing that keeps you separated from loved ones or any other host of experiences, the Detroit Historical Society wants to make sure those memories are preserved.⁠
⁠
The @detroithistorical took over management of the Detroit Historical Museum and Dossin Great Lakes Museum during Detroit’s financial crisis. It also manages an inventory of about 250,000 artifacts in the city’s archival collection.⁠
⁠
The society is now asking that people record or share their COVID-19 recollections in writing, while they are fresh.⁠
⁠
In the link in our bio, Joel Stone, senior curator, and William “Billy” Wall-Winkel, assistant curator, share the details.⁠
⁠
Photo Illustration by Maye Kuhr

¬øQu√© es la di√°stasis Abdominal?

La faja abdominal esta compuesta por un grupo muscular, los m√°s externos son los rectos abdominales mas conocidos como “abdominales”, durante el embarazo los m√∫sculos se elongan debido al crecimiento uterino, los rectos abdominales se separan debido a la disposici√≥n o direcci√≥n de sus fibras musculares, a lo que llamamos di√°stasis abdominal. Durante el postparto la di√°stasis deber√° revertir paulatinamente, pero en algunas ocasiones no revierte del todo pudiendo generar dolores lumbares, incontinencias urinarias o incluso hernias inguinales, es por esto no se recomienda realizar Crunch o Abdominales o levantarse de la cama con una flexi√≥n anterior durante el embarazo y postparto.

Navigating the normal craziness of going back to school was turned upside down by the addition of the pandemic. One of my college professors gave me some good advice. Regardless of everything happening with the world, it’s important to keep reaching for your goals. It’s so easy to let tragedy and change in general knock us down, but it’s important not to let it drown us. If your feel like life hit you full in the face and you can’t quite move past it, reach out for help from a friend or professional. Dream big and believe in yourself.

Sabtu Malam (29/08/2020) - Bupati Lampung Barat Hi. Parosil Mabsus menghadiri acara Pengesahan dan Wisuda Warga Baru Persaudaraan Setia Hati Terate (PSHT) Cabang Lampung Barat Nic 068 Pusat Madiun Angkatan 2020/2021 bertempat di Gedung PSHT Simpang Serdang Kelurahan Way Mengaku Kecamatan Balik Bukit.

Pengesahan dan Wisuda Warga Baru PSHT yang mencapai 663 orang yang lengkap dengan menggunakan protokol kesehatan covid-19 ini turut dihadiri Angoota DPRD Lambar, Perwakilan Polres Lambar, Perwakilan Kodim 0422/LB, Kasat Pol PP, Camat Balik Bukit, Lurah Way Mengaku, Ketua Cabang PSHT Kabupaten Way Kanan, Ketua Cabang PSHT Kabupaten Pesisir Barat, Ketua Cabang PSHT Lampung Utara dan Seluruh Ketua Ranting PSHT se-Lampung Barat.

Pada kesempatan ini, Bupati meminta kepada Keluarga Besar PSHT di Lampung Barat yang mencapai hingga 12.000 orang ini untuk ikut serta mendukung program pemerintah daerah dalam menciptakan Lampung Barat Hebat dan Sejahtera.
.

node.accessibility_caption: Teaching kids gratitude and patience during the trying times of covid 19
Teaching kids gratitude and patience during the trying times of covid 19

node.text:
ArtWorX had its first class today. The theme of the class was the biggest learning from COVID 19.

Yes, you guessed it right - GRATITUDE. While these are one of the toughest times the world has seen in a very long time, it has also brought the much needed yet ignored ‘gratitude’ back into fashion. 

We spoke to our Ninjas about the principles of gratitude - introspect, accept, embrace and asked them to let their neuroma flow on paper, in colours of their choice, in structures of their kind, in images of their want. To set the mood, we played ‘Red Hot Chilly Peppers’ as a background score but our Ninjas wanted to ‘Sauda Khara Khara’. Their wish was our command.

1.5 hours hence regular ice breakers forth, Picasso was born in different Avatars.

We went to take the class as mentors but guess what blue turned out to be deeper than indigo, we came back home as students.
.
.
.

node.text:
LG ha lanzado el PuriCare Wearable Air Purifier, un tapabocas el√©ctrico que purifica el aire y que, seg√∫n la empresa, ayuda a respirar mejor.
‚†Ä
La LG PuriCare Wearable Air Purifier purifica el aire que el usuario inhala, y tambi√©n “limpia” el que exhala. Para realizar esta funci√≥n, el cubrebocas est√° compuesto por un sensor de respiraci√≥n, dos filtros H13 HEPA de alta eficiencia intercambiables, dos ventiladores y una bater√≠a de 820 mAh.

Al tratarse de un dispositivo electr√≥nico, este barbijo necesitar√° que sea cargado de vez en cuando. LG asegura hasta ocho horas de uso con los ventiladores en modo bajo; mientras que su duraci√≥n m√≠nima puede ser de tan solo dos horas si se utiliza con los ventiladores en modo alto.

Adem√°s, el tapabocas viene con una funda para guardarlo y que a la vez mata los g√©rmenes que se adhieren al mismo. Para ello dispone de luces LED ultravioletas capaces de eliminarlos. Adem√°s, la funda permite cargar la bater√≠a del dispositivo, aunque todav√≠a se desconoce el tipo de carga.
‚†Ä
Otro aspecto interesante del PuriCare Wearable Air Purifier es que la funda env√≠a una notificaci√≥n al usuario, a trav√©s de la app LG ThinQ, para avisarle cuando los filtros est√°n perdiendo efectividad.
‚†Ä

Thank you Yachele for your dedication, commitment, and loyalty!  We So Appreciate You! 

Nothing makes me happier than building relationships and helping people!

Two of THE most Covet items during this Covid-19 Pandemic are the Disinfectant Wipes and Lysol Spray. 

I now have several Miracle Wipes!

I am giving them all away!  They won’t last!

Call Me!

STAY STRONG
STAY POSITIVE
STAY OPTIMISTIC

I ENCOURAGE ALL OF YOU TO HELP SOMEONE TODAY AND EVERYDAY DURING THESE VERY CHALLENGING COVID 19 TIMES! 

I am still offering my deliveries to people of need 

Who is Next!  Call Me!

I want to help more people! 

I do not charge anyone.  The people make out their lists and just pay me for their groceries.  I commend the people that ask me for help! 

Who else needs my help! I am scheduling appointments all this week.

Dog and Cat food as well!

Stay Safe Everyone!

node.text:
As days passed by, I received daily doses of realisations and an awakeing that this Duniya (world) is never permanent, it shall definitely end. I wanted my near ones to be with me always, but a verse in the Qur'an that "...Every soul shall taste death" took me a step closer to the Truth. 

In the current situation, with plenty of time at hand, I made time to study our Islamic ettiquites and tried to be punctual in all my prayers, with a hope that The Almighty will be pleased with me and I can ask Him to guide and place my near& Dear ones and the whole of humanity in the Bestest of places (Jannah). 
‚ú®
- Submitted by Bushra Fathima (Associate, GIO Blr)

node.text:
Bombay HC Rejects Bail To Stalker of Pune Girl

The Bombay High Court on Saturday refused bail to a man who was in custody for stalking and stabbing a Pune girl. 
Justice Sarang Kotwal rejected the plea citing threat to life to the girl, who the man, Amol Kashid stabbed 6 times for refusing his marriage proposal last year.
Kashid repeatedly harassed the complainant and attacked her in front of her mother and grandmother.

“Therefore it is not desirable to release the Applicant on bail,” he stated.
The man had moved the high court on grounds of completed investigation and the chargesheet being filed, because of which he was no longer required in custody.

Keunggulan Suplemennya :
1. Menghilangkan Mata Minus & Silinder pada Mata (Hasil 1-2 Minggu uda ada perubahan )
2. Memperbaiki Kecembungan Kornea pada Mata agar kembali Normal.
3. Suplemen dengan Kandungan utama Vitamin A Tinggi , Lutein , Beta Carotene , Lechitine dan Carrot Powder yg sangat baik buat Mata.
4. 1 Kapsulnya mengandung nutrisi 1 Kg Nutrisi Wortel.

node.text:
“My name is Maria. I’m from Yerwada, India and work as a daily wager in a small neighborhood grocery shop. 

I lost my job and income when the COVID-19 lockdown was imposed. My kids and I were nearly left homeless after my landlord threw us out. I’m staying with my brother now, there are 9 of us in a small house. 

Life during COVID has been unbelievably difficult for my children and me. I’m trying to get back my job, but with the lockdown, it’s tough to survive. 

During this crisis, the food basket from KCA and Saahasee has reduced my worry and burden so much. At least I don’t need to beg for food. I can try to look for a new job and possibly a new home too.”

The government and the healthcare bodies are continually requesting to stay indoors, use sanitizers frequently, stay calm, and immediately reach out for medical advice in case of showing¬†coronavirus infection symptoms—cough, fever, sneezing, fatigue, and difficulty in breathing. Amidst all these, there’s severe panic among the citizens, a lot of them relying on the fake news and messages being spread through social media regarding the coronavirus causes or modes of treatment. So we are looking at some of these misconceptions that are getting circulated and¬†busting the myths¬†around them.

.
Hari ini media sosial kembali membicarakan beliau Ustadz Ismail Yusanto¬†@yusanto_ismail¬†. Sosok yang tenang lagi bijaksana, berpenampilan khas peci hitam nusantara. Terminologi "Dakwah", "HTI", "SYARIAH" dan KHILAFAH tentu melekat pada figur bersahaja karena orang mengenal poros hidupnya untuk itu.

.
Kini ada manusia jalang yang mencoba menghalangi langkahnya. Kembali difitnah dan diperkarakan serta dicari kesalahannya.

.
Bagi mereka yang punya niat jahat, bertaubatlah. Bagi kita semua, hayatilah puisi renungan beliau ini. Maka, ketegaran dan semangat dakwah akan selalu menggelora, jika seandainya beliau menjadi korban kedzoliman.

.
Dan hari ini kita sedang hidup di masa mulkan jabbriyyan (penguasa-penguasa yang memaksakan kehendak), tetapi masa ini akan segera kita lewati. Pada akhirnya kita akan hidup kembali di masa #khilafah 'ala minhajin nubuwwah (khilafah yang sesuai dengan metode kenabian). Ini adalah janji Allah SWT dan bisyarah Rasulullah SAW yang tidak seorang pun bisa menghalangi. Sekuat dan setinggi apapun kedudukannya, sebanyak apapun hartanya tidak akan ¬†pernah bisa menghalangi kembalinya khilafah ¬†Islam. Sehingga semakin dibungkam, semakin kemenangan itu akan Allah SWT segerakan. Aamiin.
